Install the following

JDK
Jenkins
Maven
Apache-tomcat


go to system properties>>Advanced tab>> environment variables>>change the path >>> include maven, JDK, git



system variabkes>>>include JDK

Jenkins>> Global tool configuration>>> include Maven, JDK & GIT Path





Under jenkins provide the following URL

Create Project<name> free style

in Source Code Management choose GIT and provide the URL of the GIT hub repository

in Build choose Maven and in the goals type "clean install"




for deployment 

type **/*.war in post build actions

Context Path - give some name 

in containers

choose tomcat8.x

provide the tomcat credentials
and the tomcat URL : http://localhost:8899/





